  <section id="faq">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
    <div class="faq-item">
      <input type="checkbox" id="faq1" class="faq-toggle">
      <label for="faq1" class="faq-question">1. What is Steed Media?</label>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Steed Media is the UK’s leading provider of state-of-the-art mechanical horses for film, TV, and creative productions. Our highly realistic animatronic horses are designed to deliver safe, reliable, and lifelike performances, saving production teams time and eliminating the challenges of working with live animals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
    <div class="faq-item">
      <input type="checkbox" id="faq2" class="faq-toggle">
      <label for="faq2" class="faq-question">2. Why choose a mechanical horse over a real horse?</label>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Mechanical horses offer numerous advantages for film and TV productions:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Enhanced Safety:</strong> No risk to actors or crew during stunts or close-contact scenes. Establishing shots and wides can then be done with doubles or stuntmen on real horses.</li>
          <li><strong>Consistent Motion:</strong> Perfectly repeatable movements for multiple takes.</li>
          <li><strong>Unmatched Versatility:</strong> Works indoors, outdoors, and on challenging terrain without concerns about fatigue or behaviour.</li>
          <li><strong>Cost Savings:</strong> Avoid the expense of animal handlers, veterinary care, and transport logistics.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
    <div class="faq-item">
      <input type="checkbox" id="faq3" class="faq-toggle">
      <label for="faq3" class="faq-question">3. How lifelike are your mechanical horses?</label>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Our mechanical horses are engineered to replicate the appearance, movements, and anatomy of real horses. Key features include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Realistic Coats:</strong> Customisable, high-quality materials for natural-looking manes, tails, and fur.</li>
          <li><strong>Accurate Anatomy:</strong> Proportions and muscle definition designed for both close-up and wide shots.</li>
          <li><strong>Custom Colour Matching:</strong> Horses can be matched to the colour of real horses in your production, with manes and tails designed to blend perfectly for continuity.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Continue adding all FAQ items as needed -->

    <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
    <div class="faq-item">
      <input type="checkbox" id="faq4" class="faq-toggle">
      <label for="faq4" class="faq-question">4. What kind of movements can the mechanical horses perform?</label>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Our mechanical horses are pre-set with cinematic-grade motion sequences, offering versatility for a wide range of scenes. Key movement features include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Lifelike Gaits:</strong> Walking, trotting, and galloping, with smooth transitions between movements.</li>
          <li><strong>Head and Neck Dynamics:</strong> Natural bobbing, turning, and tilting for realistic interaction.</li>
          <li><strong>Stunt Performance:</strong> While the horses do not rear, they are ideal for action-packed stunt scenes, including controlled falls, rigging for wire work, and supporting stunt performers during complex sequences. Save time in complex rigging sequences prep because it can be placed in the exact place and action repeated over and over exactly the same.</li>
          <li><strong>Silent Operation:</strong> Quiet mechanics ensure no disruption to on-set audio recording.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
    <div class="faq-item">
      <input type="checkbox" id="faq5" class="faq-toggle">
      <label for="faq5" class="faq-question">5. Are your mechanical horses safe and enjoyable for actors of all ages?</label>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Yes! Our mechanical horses are designed to be safe and enjoyable for both children and adults. Key features include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Sturdy Mounts:</strong> Are built for maximum stability, ensuring a secure experience for riders of all ages. The horses are mounted on the front with an airbag which assists in getting heads in the correct position for the camera and comfort for the rider.</li>
          <li><strong>Smooth, Gentle Motion:</strong> The horses’ movements are predictable and comfortable, making them ideal for actors performing long or complex scenes.</li>
          <li><strong>Custom Protective Options:</strong> Additional padding, harnesses, and other safety features are available to meet specific needs.</li>
          <li><strong>Exciting and Realistic Design:</strong> Children and adults alike enjoy working with our lifelike horses, which help them stay immersed in their roles and deliver authentic performances.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

