    <h2><strong>Logistics and Delivery</strong></h2>

    <!-- FAQ Item 9 -->
    <div class="faq-item">
      <input type="checkbox" id="faq9" class="faq-toggle">
      <label for="faq9" class="faq-question">9. How is the mechanical horse delivered and mounted?</label>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Our mechanical horses are transported using a 4x4 Land Cruiser and a large trailer. Each delivery includes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>A petrol-powered Can-am All-terrain vehicle.</li>
          <li>Up to 6 mechanical horses and 1 rehearsal horse delivered per trip, depending on your production’s needs.</li>
          <li>A dedicated technician and driver to ensure safe delivery, installation, and setup.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>The horses themselves do not require electricity and are designed for simple, efficient operation. The quad-mounted system allows the horse to be repositioned to the left, right, or centre for dynamic camera angles. There are seats for crew front and back which are interchangeable, facing forward and backwards. Additionally, horses can be mounted on larger vehicles or stationary rigs for controlled or dynamic filming.</p>
        <p>The trailer includes a workshop for on-site adjustments or maintenance, which requires either mains electricity or battery power for operation, ensuring flexibility at any filming location. The workshop also stores the Can-am and horses when not in use.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Item 10 -->
    <div class="faq-item">
      <input type="checkbox" id="faq10" class="faq-toggle">
      <label for="faq10" class="faq-question">10. Do you ship internationally?</label>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Yes, we provide international shipping and logistical support. Additional fees for customs and transport may apply.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Item 11 -->
    <div class="faq-item">
      <input type="checkbox" id="faq11" class="faq-toggle">
      <label for="faq11" class="faq-question">11. What are the power requirements?</label>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>The horses themselves do not require power. However, the trailer workshop can be powered by standard mains electricity or battery packs if needed for on-site adjustments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Item 12 -->
    <div class="faq-item">
      <input type="checkbox" id="faq12" class="faq-toggle">
      <label for="faq12" class="faq-question">12. How long does it take to set up the mechanical horse on set?</label>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Setup times vary depending on the scene requirements, but our team ensures a fast and efficient setup process. Most installations take between 30 minutes to a few hours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

