    <h2><strong>Safety</strong></h2>

    <!-- FAQ Item 13 -->
    <div class="faq-item">
      <input type="checkbox" id="faq13" class="faq-toggle">
      <label for="faq13" class="faq-question">13. Are your mechanical horses safe to use on set?</label>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Yes, safety is a top priority. Our mechanical horses undergo rigorous testing and meet the highest safety standards. We also provide on-site safety briefings for the entire crew. We have up-to-date inspections for rig, risk assessments, and insurance that covers our equipment and people.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Item 14 -->
    <div class="faq-item">
      <input type="checkbox" id="faq14" class="faq-toggle">
      <label for="faq14" class="faq-question">14. What happens if the mechanical horse malfunctions?</label>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>In the rare event of a malfunction, our on-set technicians are trained to quickly resolve any issues to minimise downtime. Replacement units can also be provided if necessary.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

